        "**5 Points Derivative - End**\n",
        "\n",
        "$\\frac{df(x_{o})}{dx} =  \\frac{-25f(x_{o}) \\;+\\; 48f(x_{o} + h) \\; - \\;36f(x_{o} + 2h) \\; + \\; 16f(x_{o} + 3h) \\; - \\;3f(x_{o} + 4h}{12h} $\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
